<h1
  class="text-center text-lg font-bold py-4"
>
  AutoTamizaje
</h1>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center">
  <div class="flex flex-col w-4/5">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto sm:-mx-6 lg:-mx-8">
      <div class="inline-block py-2 min-w-full sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="overflow-hidden shadow-md sm:rounded-lg">
          <table class="min-w-full">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700">
              <tr>
              <th scope="col" class="py-3 px-6 text-xs font-medium tracking-wider text-left text-gray-700 uppercase dark:text-gray-400">
                Tus datos de tamizaje
              </th>
              <th scope="col" class="py-3 px-6 text-xs font-medium tracking-wider text-left text-gray-700 uppercase text-blue-400">
                <a href="/edit">Editar</a>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="bg-white border-b dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">
                  Mail UC
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-gray-400">
                  <%= current_user.email %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white border-b dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">
                  Contraseña UC
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-gray-400">
                  ********
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white border-b dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">
                  Campus
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-gray-400">
                  <%= current_user.campus %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white border-b dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">
                  Lugar del Campus
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-gray-400">
                  <%= current_user.campus_place %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white border-b dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">
                  Tipo de miembro UC
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-gray-400">
                  <%= current_user.uc_member_type %>
                </td>
              </tr>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">
                  Activo
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-gray-400">
                  <%= current_user.active ? 'Sí' : 'No' %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white border-b dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
              <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">
                  Días de tamizaje
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-gray-400">
                  <%= current_user.scraping_days.map(&:weekday).join(', ') %>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-orange-100 border-l-4 border-orange-500 text-orange-700 p-4" role="alert">
      <p class="font-bold">Atención</p>
      <p>Éste bot es una versión en progreso. Espero que eventualmente ande sin problemas todos los días. Actualmente, puede fallar algunos días.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h1
    class="text-center text-lg font-bold py-4"
  >
    Historial
  </h1>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto sm:-mx-6 lg:-mx-8">
      <div class="inline-block py-2 min-w-full sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="overflow-hidden shadow-md sm:rounded-lg">
          <table class="min-w-full">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700">
              <tr>
              <th scope="col" class="py-3 px-6 text-xs font-medium tracking-wider text-left text-gray-700 uppercase dark:text-gray-400">
                Fecha
              </th>
              <th scope="col" class="py-3 px-6 text-xs font-medium tracking-wider text-left text-gray-700 uppercase text-gray-400">
                Estado
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <% current_user.scraping_intents.last(5).each do |intent| %>
                <tr class="bg-white border-b dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
                  <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">
                    <%= intent.created_at.localtime.to_formatted_s(:short) %>
                  </td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-6 text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap dark:text-gray-400">
                    <%= intent.state %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              <% end %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
